{"tid":2079612,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無港大讀QFin或者有讀QFin既巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2020-06-26T01:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T02:59:00.000Z","uid":132194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f88d7c23396ce14752494c23529db448afac8091","tid":2079612,"uid":132194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:56:28.000Z","msg":"小弟本科算係it related. 呢架讀緊postgrad. 計劃緊末來工作上要入邊一行<br />\n<br />\n其實心中一直都想對金融呢行都有興趣，<br />\n所以想係畢業之前去研究一下香港大學教QFin係教啲咩。 <br />\n<br />\n經過左一輪基本研究之後<br />\n我發現真正同finance有關既course其實好少<br />\n甚至有啲科根本就IT科黎<br />\n<br />\n以港大QFin為例 我覺得以下呢幾科係幾值得深入研究下 <br />\n1. FINA2320 Investments and portfolio analysis 6<br />\r\n2. FINA2322 Derivatives<br />\n3. Credit Risk<br />\n<br />\n除左呢幾科之外 有啲咩大topic其實係要識？<br />\n有無少少意見比下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\nBig data analytics applied toward quantitative finance呢科有幾多成係講qfin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2179ede64babe5a95c11f33262f7342ebec37e6","tid":2079612,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvShsP6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvShsP6.jpg&h=8015ac4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"},{"pid":"7be3759ed2e281bc7df4ba6405f37c8df496c6cb","tid":2079612,"uid":186661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"其實你可以睇吓EIE嗰邊<br />\n嗰邊仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀到你唔想讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74652f32cfc4a995a2bb3eee738b6304f0764048","tid":2079612,"uid":247019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T02:11:25.000Z",